sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServe as KServe Ingress<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant APIServer as vLLM API Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant AuthMW as AuthenticationMiddleware<br/>API Key Validation
    participant Engine as AsyncLLM Engine (V1)<br/>PagedAttention
    participant Executor as Model Executor<br/>CPU (OpenBLAS)
    participant HFHub as Hugging Face Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over HFHub,Executor: Flow 2: Model Loading at Startup
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Executor->>HFHub: GET model weights & tokenizer<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (HF_TOKEN)
        HFHub-->>Executor: Model Artifacts
        Note over Executor: Load into CPU Memory<br/>Initialize KV Cache<br/>(PagedAttention)
    end

    Note over Client,Executor: Flow 1: OpenAI Chat Completion Request
    rect rgb(245, 255, 245)
        Client->>KServe: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
        KServe->>APIServer: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000
        APIServer->>AuthMW: Validate API Key
        AuthMW-->>APIServer: Authorized
        APIServer->>Engine: Submit inference request<br/>Python async (in-process)
        Engine->>Executor: Execute model forward pass<br/>Python (in-process)
        Note over Executor: CPU inference<br/>OpenBLAS / numactl
        Executor-->>Engine: Token output
        Engine-->>APIServer: Generated tokens
        APIServer-->>KServe: SSE Stream response<br/>HTTP/8000
        KServe-->>Client: JSON/SSE Response<br/>HTTPS/443
    end

    Note over Client,Executor: Flow 1b: Streaming Variant
    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Client->>KServe: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>stream: true
        KServe->>APIServer: Forward
        APIServer->>Engine: Submit request
        loop Token-by-token generation
            Engine->>Executor: Forward pass
            Executor-->>Engine: Next token
            Engine-->>APIServer: Token event
            APIServer-->>KServe: SSE chunk
            KServe-->>Client: SSE data event
        end
        APIServer-->>KServe: SSE [DONE]
        KServe-->>Client: SSE [DONE]
    end

    Note over Executor,S3: Alternative: S3 Model Loading (Tensorizer)
    rect rgb(255, 245, 245)
        Executor->>S3: GET model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM (S3_ACCESS_KEY_ID)
        S3-->>Executor: Serialized model
    end
